      "title": "Fuel unloading continues, CPC says no shortage",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Ceylon Petroleum Corporation (CPC) says that the vessel carrying 30,000 MT of diesel has been unloaded.",
        "Also, another vessel carrying 37,000 MT of diesel is to be unloaded, said the CPC.",
        "Therefore, the Ceylon Petroleum Corporation (CPC) noted that there will be NO short supply of diesel and petrol."
